Vukani Community Development (Vukani) Chairperson, Mayibuye Mandela – who is also the great grandson of the late struggle icon and first democratically elected President of South Africa (SA), Nelson Mandela – will be attending a Mass Prayer Service for the Public Protecter, Busisiwe Mkhwebane, in Mpumalanga under the following details: Date: 30 August 2019 Time: 10h00 Venue: KwaMhlanga Showgrounds, Mpumalanga  Vukani will be praying for government to stop the witch-hunt against Advocate Mkhwebane and to allow her to continue serving the people as the Public Protector. Issued by the Board of Vukani Community Development 29 August 2019 For media enquiries contact: Mayibuye Melisizwe Mandela
Chairperson
